right in my kill zone.

960
01:32:01,315 --> 01:32:03,592
Now you're right in my kill zone.

961
01:32:04,685 --> 01:32:06,825
Fucking Beckett.

962
01:32:12,593 --> 01:32:14,528
(EXHALES)

963
01:32:25,139 --> 01:32:27,106
Two shots, one kill.

964
01:32:27,107 --> 01:32:29,275
You slipping, Master Guns?

965
01:32:29,276 --> 01:32:31,211
It was intended.

966
01:32:31,712 --> 01:32:34,147
The first shot was
just to let him know.

967
01:32:34,148 --> 01:32:36,118
Let him know?

968
01:32:36,283 --> 01:32:40,687
Yeah, let him know
he was about to die.

969
